ups-pi-node (0.2.1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Switch local package builds from timestamp versions to Debian revisions.
  * Add manual Wi-Fi scan action to the portal.
  * Restore ST7735 backlight control on GPIO18 and initialize it after the
    display driver.
  * Prevent system helper stop from deadlocking inside socketserver shutdown.
  * Migrate existing node configs with the ST7735 display defaults.
  * Hold the ST7735 backlight high using the same setup/output order as the
    verified hardware test.

 -- Pavlo <pavlo@example.com>  Thu, 14 May 2026 14:20:00 +0300

ups-pi-node (0.2.0) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Restore hardware UPS control through the system helper service.
  * Add ST7735 display support, helper-side PAM login, and hotspot password
    settings.
  * Enable Raspberry Pi I2C/SPI hardware buses during package setup.
  * Package the app for Debian Trixie with venv-based Python dependencies.

 -- Pavlo <pavlo@example.com>  Thu, 14 May 2026 13:30:00 +0300

